tyle=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持最大共享显示内存至1 GB</li>\r\n            </ol>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"left\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 10px; background-color: rgb(233,245,254); margin: 0px; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(61,61,61); font-size: 12px; border-top: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; font-weight: bold; border-right: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; padding-top: 10px\">音效</td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 10px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; border-top: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(149,149,149) 1px solid; padding-top: 10px\">\r\n            <ol style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n                <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">内建Realtek<sup style=\"vertical-align: text-top\">&reg;</sup>ALC898芯片</li>\r\n                <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持High Definition Audio</li>\r\n                <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持2/4/5.1/7.1声道</li>\r\n                <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: decimal; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持S/PDIF输入/输出</li>\r\n            </ol>\r\n            </td